13
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:20,240
<i>♪ My love must be hidden</i>
<i>I can hardly stand it ♪</i>

14
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:23,160
<i>♪ It's torture when you cry ♪</i>

15
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:27,040
