<i>♪ I try not to love you</i>
<i>Holding back my tears while saying goodbye ♪</i>

18
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:41,840
<i>♪ But I could never do it for real ♪</i>

19
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,840
<i>I used to date the doctor.</i>

20
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,320
<i>Used to date?</i>

21
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,640
<i>Don't tell me that</i>

22
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:51,880
<i>you've reconnected with</i>
<i>your old flame last night?</i>

23
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:54,040
<i>Serving the food before</i>
<i>the guest even arrives.</i>

24
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,440
I’ve ordered your
favorite food in advance.

25
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,840
<i>Fried boiled egg</i>
<i>with tamarind sauce, my favorite.</i>

26
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,040
What do you want?

27
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,440
I’m courting Earn,

28
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,120
