29
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,160
<i>Are you only here</i>
<i>to find the cell phone?</i>

30
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,040
<i>Why do I have to stay?</i>

31
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,320
Just accompany me.

32
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,880
Unless you’re afraid
of your own feelings.

33
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,000
Why bother with all the effort to cook?

34
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:32,040
I don't want to eat with you.

35
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,920
Okay.

36
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,320
Make way, please.

37
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,840
Fine, I'll taste it for you.

38
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,720
I can tell it's not delicious.

39
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,640
It's not tasty at all. Bland.

40
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,720
Is it really that delicious?

41
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,400
Not delicious.

42
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,240
Your expression, though.

43
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,480
I said it's not delicious.

44
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,120
It's not delicious.
You don't have to eat it.

45
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,760
-I wasn't going to eat it anyway.
-You don't have to eat it.

46
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,440
I wasn't going to eat it anyway.

47
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,840
I said I'm not eating...

48
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,720
Eat.

49
