53
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,360
This piece.

54
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,640
Here.

55
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:17,160
Oh, wow.

56
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,760
