-A secret?

70
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,920
Can someone like me complete it?

71
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,840
Even with a reference,

72
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,200
I still can't do it.

73
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,160
You can complete it.

74
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,440
You can do it.

75
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,840
And after you finish it,

76
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,280
you'll see that this picture is

77
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:30,800
very important for our relationship.

78
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,400
Really?

79
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,120
Uh-huh.

80
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:29,200
Look at this. This is my dream house.

81
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,680
I dream that one day

82
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:33,000
I'll own this house.

83
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,200
This

84
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,800
must be expensive.

85
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,480
Doctor,

86
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,320
is this

87
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,560
our house?

88
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,840
I'm heading back.

89
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:36,960
What's going on?

90
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,440
Doctor.

91
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,360
Doctor!

92
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,000
Drive safely,

93
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,040
