94
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,160
What are you doing, Lada?

95
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,200
Stay focused!

96
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:30,840
Stay focused!

97
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,760
Losing again and again.

98
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,240
Lada!

99
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,720
New lipstick, right?

100
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:48,440
It looks nice.

101
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,360
Did you hear that?

102
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,240
I'm not imagining things, right?

103
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,280
Confirmed.

104
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:16,600
She still remembers I like white lilies.

105
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,160
So good at making up.

106
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,360
Do you like them, Lada?

107
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,280
When I bought them,

108
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,600
I just thought they looked pretty.

109
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,680
But if you like them, I'm happy.

110
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:35,400
These are from you, Nu?

111
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,120
Thank you.

112
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:41,040
You have another patient appointment
this evening, right?

113
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:43,320
So, please have coffee with me.

114
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,640
Then please

115
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,520
