for about five minutes.

116
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,720
Sure.

117
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:04,800
FRIENDS
SOS. I NEED URGENT HELP

118
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,360
Here you go.

119
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,560
But usually I see you
drinking black coffee.

120
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,200
Why did you drink orange juice today?

121
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,680
Oh,

122
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,640
I've run out of my coffee quota.

123
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,280
I only have one glass per day.

124
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:22,040
Ah okay,

125
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,760
I'll note this down then.

126
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,560
Then please note down my details too.

127
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:30,680
I drink less sweetened cappuccino
in case I gain weight.

128
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:34,360
Less sweetened cappuccino
to avoid gaining weight?

129
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:38,280
But you also drink boba tea
and sweet Chinese Pastry,

130
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:39,480
I guess it's not fat at all?

131
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:41,200
-And what about you...
-Enough!

132
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:43,760
How long are you all
going to argue over my head?

133
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,800
Sit down. Sit.

134
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,400
You're doing fine right, Bow, Mr. Tan?

135
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,480
Whenever I come here

136
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,480
I always see you two together.

137
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,720
Ah, you see,

138
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:02,840
we just happen to be quite close,
the three of us.

139
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,960
We always go places together.

140
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,120
Bow,

141
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:09,360
