142
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:16,800
Hello.

143
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,120
Pardon me?

144
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,960
Is it an emergency case?

145
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,600
How is the patient?

146
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:27,400
Okay, I'll hurry over now.

147
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,440
Should I give you
the Golden Globe Award?

148
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,960
I've done my job,

149
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,840
you figure out how
to escape by yourself.

150
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,160
Please excuse me.

151
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,360
Sure.

152
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,320
Take care then.

153
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,200
Uh oh!

154
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:49,880
Oh, it's my cell phone.

155
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,920
Oh my god, you need me?

156
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,520
Oh, okay, I'll hurry over now.

157
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,800
Hey,

158
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,960
I have to go too.

159
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,320
Sure.

160
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,000
Please excuse me.

161
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:11,760
Normally the skin doctors emergencies

162
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:13,240
happen every day?

163
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,359
Uhh...

164
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,880
You see...

165
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,000
Your americano is ready.

166
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:20,400
I'll get it for you.

167
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,599
It's okay, I'll get it myself.

168
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,800
No, it's fine, it's nothing.

169
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,960
It's okay, I ordered it.

170
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,119
It's really okay!

171
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:26,960
-It's no problem.
-I'll get it for you.

172
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,920
-Really it's fine.
-No, it's okay.

173
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:29,960
Whoa!

174
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,560
Ugh!

175
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:32,840
Oh no!

176
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:34,560
Ugh!

177
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,840
My apologies.

178
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,520
I'm sorry.

179
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,920
You can go change into my shirt first

180
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,400
and you can return it later.

181
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,160
Thank you.

182
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,880
I can do it myself.

183
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,480
It's okay, I'm a doctor.

184
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:54,880
Did you forget

185
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,440
that I'm a doctor

186
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:58,960
too?

187
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,520
You're right.

188
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,000
Here you go.

189
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:31,240
I'll wash and return it to you.

190
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:33,360
Okay.

191
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,160
What got into me?

192
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,440
Good morning, everyone.

193
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:00,040
We're here!

194
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:02,960
Hey,

195
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:05,520
she bought everything at the market.

196
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,360
Amazing, Mother.

197
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:09,920
Distribute this, even give some to Wang.

198
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:11,640
He eats a lot. Give these to him.

199
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:12,840
Oh, that's too much.

200
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,320
I haven't picked anything yet.

201
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,240
-Let me choose first.
-Mother.

202
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:17,720
You need to be nourished.

203
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,400
Here, take this.

204
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,920
Here.

205
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:21,920
Wow.

206
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,920
Eat it all, okay?

207
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,200
Oh, let's eat together later.

208
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,560
Come.

209
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:31,000
You sit and do your makeup first.

210
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:34,560
How are you?

211
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,840
You seem to be in a good mood today.

212
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,800
When good things happen,

213
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,120
you should be in a good mood, right?

214
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,960
So, if good things happen,

215
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:45,000
I hope you won't forget about me.

216
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,360
Whatever you want,

217
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:48,840
just tell me,

218
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:50,080
and I'll take care of it for you.

219
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:50,760
Really?

220
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:51,800
Yes.

221
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:54,080
But I don't want money or sweets.

222
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:01,560
Kiss me on the cheek as a reward.

223
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:14,200
Do you want it like
in the drama or in real life?

224
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,040
In real life.

225
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:26,280
Hey!

226
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:29,080
Are my nails pretty?

227
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:31,320
Your nails are very pretty, sis.

228
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,600
What are you doing?

229
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:33,640
Just teasing.

230
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,000
Oh,

231
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:35,880
teasing.

232
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,160
You're teasing too much.

233
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,560
She's just been weaned.

234
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:39,360
Weaned!

235
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:41,240
-Weaned!
-Weaned!

236
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:52,800
Let's change clothes.

237
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,120
Let's change clothes.

238
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,280
I'll be right back.

239
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:57,120
I'll take her to change clothes.

240
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,240
Sure.

241
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,160
Which one, Mother?

242
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:17,440
-Hey!
-Earn!

243
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:19,240
Cut, cut, cut!

244
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:20,960
Ratee!

245
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,200
Check on her.

246
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,040
Ratee!

247
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,640
Tell me if you're hurt anywhere.

248
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,880
My leg.

249
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,160
Hey.

250
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:32,080
Did you mess up the cue again, Ratee?

251
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,560
I didn't mean to.

252
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:35,480
How was I supposed to know
this would happen?

253
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:36,840
I don't believe you.

254
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,040
We practiced the cue already.

255
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,880
What's this?
Are you afraid of the effects?

256
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:41,160
You fell and hit Earn.

257
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,160
If it wasn't intentional,
what do you call that?

258
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,360
I call it bad luck.

259
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:45,800
I was working just fine,

260
00:22:45,840 --> 00:22:46,880
and something happened.

261
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,240
Want to know what that something is?

262
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,520
I can arrange it for you.

263
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,960
Geez.

264
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,320
You hurt someone else

265
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,480
and still don't feel guilty.

266
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:55,080
Isn't this going too far?

267
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:55,800
Stop.

268
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:57,520
-Why?
-Or you won't get to breathe again.

269
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:59,560
-Bring it on!
-Bring it on!

270
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:01,160
Calm down, everyone.

271
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,440
Ratee,

272
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,200
even if it wasn't intentional,

273
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,720
you messed up the cue.

274
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:10,920
Look, your friend is hurt,

275
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:13,880
and I haven't heard
a single apology from you.

276
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:17,880
Sorry.

277
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:20,200
Hey, why not wait until the next life?

278
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,000
