308
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:31,800
Please.

309
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:32,840
Doctor.

310
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,760
Please calm down.

311
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:35,800
I will take care of her.

312
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:37,520
