313
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,440
This way please.

314
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:53,800
Doctor.

315
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,800
Prepare the stitching equipment.

316
00:24:57,840 --> 00:24:58,840
Yes, Doctor.

317
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:06,960
It's okay.

318
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,720
I'll give you a local anesthetic.

319
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,960
