Very good.

324
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:05,440
Don't cry.

325
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:07,480
I'll make the stitches nice and neat.

326
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,080
Just a little.

327
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:33,080
Just a little more and it will be done.

328
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:53,280
Does it hurt?

329
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,400
It still hurts a little.

330
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:02,040
But I want to keep feeling this way.

331
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:04,040
Why?

332
00:27:05,080 --> 00:27:06,600
So you'll pay attention to me.

333
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:12,520
Hmm?

334
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,520
Oh!

335
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:38,320
